name: The Five Door Hanover Sideboard
description: A classic signature style Davidson sideboard, the five door Hanover elevates any interior by its elegant chamfered edged frame and superior quality of finishing. This large side cabinet is available in any of Davidson's beautiful collection of high gloss and satin finishes with nickel and brass options to choose from. The cabinet is available in any of DAVIDSON's gorgeous timber finishes with a stunning radial pattern, now synonymous with Davidson furniture. Shown here with five push latch doors, the cabinet boasts a metal trim for an extra touch of opulence, all standing on a well proportioned facetted base. The interior of the cabinet opens to reveal a satin interior with two adjustable shelves, with bespoke options available upon request. This five door Hanover cabinet would complete any dining room, lounge, kitchen or bedroom setting and is ideal for both private and commercial projects.
